&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Leadership &lt;/strong&gt;– As a lead, you enjoy mentoring others, providing guidance and leadership to your team. Additionally, you will help the Neighborhood achieve their financial goals through managing costs and being resourceful. You lead by example, setting the standard for the team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
