&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px;&quot;&gt;Some companies call them “Assistant Property Managers” or &quot;Assistant Business Managers&quot;, but at Prometheus our Leasing &amp;amp; Experience Managers do so much more. As a Leasing &amp;amp; Experience Manager, your role is a constant blend of:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Neighbor Relations -&lt;/strong&gt; If you love helping people, building relationships, planning events, and providing five-star quality customer service than this position is for you. You will present a professional approach to remedy any Neighbor concerns and follow-up as necessary to ensure the Ultimate Neighbor Experience.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Leasing Activities&lt;/strong&gt; - You&#39;re already a leasing All-Star and in this position, you will assist other Neighbor Ambassadors with closing. Additionally, you will help create strategic sales and marketing programs to maximize rental activity, developing an intimate knowledge of market conditions.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Daily Operations&lt;/strong&gt; - You will take a proactive role in the preparation and maintenance of Neighbor profiles. You&#39;ll assist with pricing, concessions, occupancy reporting, and collections.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Supervisory Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt; - You will supervise the leasing team, provide general training &amp;amp; development, and set goals &amp;amp; celebrate milestones. We love to have fun while we work and celebrate each other!&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
